# Code owners for security-critical paths.
#
# NOTE: this file only enforces required review once branch protection on `main`
# has "Require review from Code Owners" enabled in GitHub → Settings → Branches.
# Until then it documents intent. The point is that changes to the CI security
# gates and their scripts cannot be weakened in the same PR without an owner's
# review.

# CI workflows and their helper scripts (the security gates themselves).
/.github/workflows/   @habibClearview
/.github/scripts/     @habibClearview
/.github/CODEOWNERS   @habibClearview

# Server-side authentication & authorization helpers.
/src/lib/auth/        @habibClearview

# CodeRabbit review configuration.
/.coderabbit.yaml     @habibClearview

# PR template — carries the security/auth definition-of-done checklist.
/.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md   @habibClearview
